graph TB
    subgraph DSPO["Data Science Pipelines Operator"]
        Controller["DSPAReconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Templating["Manifestival Templating<br/>(config/internal/ templates)"]
        HealthCheck["Health Check System<br/>(DB + S3 probes)"]
        ManagedPipelines["Managed Pipelines Fetcher<br/>(OCI image manifest)"]
        Controller -->|renders| Templating
        Controller -->|probes backends| HealthCheck
        Controller -->|fetches manifests| ManagedPipelines
    end

    User["User / Data Scientist"] -->|creates| DSPACR["DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR"]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller

    subgraph DSPStack["DSP Stack (per DSPA namespace)"]
        APIServer["ds-pipeline-api-server<br/>8888/TCP REST, 8887/TCP gRPC"]
        KubeRBACProxy["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(sidecar) 8443/TCP"]
        PersistenceAgent["ds-pipeline-persistenceagent"]
        ScheduledWF["ds-pipeline-scheduledworkflow"]
        ArgoWFCtrl["ds-pipeline-workflow-controller<br/>(Argo)"]
        MLMDgRPC["ds-pipeline-metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC"]
        MLMDEnvoy["ds-pipeline-metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP + kube-rbac-proxy"]
        Webhook["ds-pipelines-webhook<br/>8443/TCP (conditional)"]
        InitManagedPipelines["init-managed-pipelines<br/>(init container)"]
    end

    Templating -->|deploys| APIServer
    Templating -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Templating -->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    Templating -->|deploys| ArgoWFCtrl
    Templating -->|deploys| MLMDgRPC
    Templating -->|deploys| MLMDEnvoy
    Templating -->|deploys| Webhook

    APIServer --- KubeRBACProxy
    InitManagedPipelines -->|loads pipelines| APIServer

    subgraph OptionalBackends["Optional Managed Backends"]
        MariaDB["MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP"]
        MinIO["MinIO<br/>9000/TCP"]
    end

    Templating -.->|deploys - optional| MariaDB
    Templating -.->|deploys - optional| MinIO

    subgraph ExternalBackends["External Backends"]
        ExtDB["External Database<br/>(MySQL/MariaDB)"]
        ExtS3["External S3 Store"]
    end

    APIServer -->|metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|metadata| ExtDB
    APIServer -->|artifacts| MinIO
    APIServer -->|artifacts| ExtS3
    MLMDgRPC -->|lineage data| MariaDB
    MLMDgRPC -->|lineage data| ExtDB

    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| APIServer
    ScheduledWF -->|creates Workflows| ArgoWFCtrl
    ArgoWFCtrl -->|orchestrates| PipelinePods["Pipeline Pods<br/>(launcher/driver)"]
    PipelinePods -->|lineage| MLMDgRPC
    PipelinePods -->|artifacts| MinIO
    PipelinePods -->|artifacts| ExtS3

    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicies["NetworkPolicies"]
    Controller -->|creates| Routes["OpenShift Routes<br/>(TLS Reencrypt)"]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceMonitors["ServiceMonitors"]

    ManagedPipelines -->|fetches| OCIRegistry["OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP"]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Templating fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style HealthCheck fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style ManagedPipelines fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#9b59b6,color:#fff
    style PersistenceAgent fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style ScheduledWF fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style ArgoWFCtrl fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style MLMDgRPC fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style MLMDEnvoy fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style MariaDB fill:#e67e22,color:#fff
    style MinIO fill:#e67e22,color:#fff
    style ExtDB fill:#999,color:#fff
    style ExtS3 fill:#999,color:#fff
    style OCIRegistry fill:#999,color:#fff
